dct_title_s: Plan showing property to be acquired from the Cape May Sand Company for the ferry between Cape May Point and Lewes, Delaware
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Alexander Avenue to Sunset Boulevard in Lower Township. Map shows lots owned by the Cape May Sand Company along with lots owned by private citizens. The exterior line for solid fill and piers and the high water line are drawn on the map.
dcat_keyword_sm: Delaware Bay  Del. and  --Cape May County--Lower Township
